Description
COVID-19: Provides assistance with rent and rental arrears to families and individuals affected by the pandemic crisis; Financial assistance availability when funding is made available.

Eligibility requirements:

Residents:
Must meet federal income eligibility requirements;
Must provide identification for all household members;
Must provide documentation of household income;
Landlords:
Must agree to receive rental payments and end eviction process;
Must fill out a W-9 form;
Will receive back rental payments directly from Bethany House of Laredo.

